#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/config/updating_iot.rst:183
msgid ""
"If a new version of the :abbr:`IoT (Internet of Things)` box image is "
"available, an :guilabel:`Upgrade to _xx.xx_` button appears at the bottom of"
